{{flavour|Intensifies the natural venom of the target monster. Poisonous bites and spit become intense enough to slow and asphyxiate.}}

'''Concentrate Venom''' is a monster-only spell that imbues the target's natural venom with [[curare]] properties. Affected abilities include [[venom]]-branded attacks and [[Spit Poison]].

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Concentrate Venom was introduced in [[0.27]].

